claim.claim-text:
12. A phase-change optical recording medium, comprising: 
a reflective/heat dissipating layer provided contiguously to at least one surface of a recording layer, having a dielectric protective layer interposed between said reflective/heat dissipating layer and said recording layer; 
wherein said recording layer essentially consists of a phase-change recording material having a Sb3Te meta-stable phase, said dielectric protective layer essentially consists of a dielectric material containing ZrO2 as a major ingredient, and said reflective/heat dissipating layer essentially consists of Ag, as a major ingredient.
